title: Michigan DE Aidan Hutchinson Stops By The Show
description:
Jalen & Jacoby discuss Giannis’ total destruction of the Lakers, Russell Westbrook gets benched again, chances an Harden-Simmons trade happen before the deadline, plus Aidan Hutchinson stops by to talk Michigan football, NFL Draft, Super Bowl LVI and much more.
